Class ResolvedTuple.ResolvedMap

java.lang.Object

public abstract static class ResolvedTuple.ResolvedMap extends ResolvedTuple
Represents a map implied by the project list, whether or not the map actually appears in the table schema. The column is implied to be a map because it contains children. This implementation builds the map and its children.
